{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socketprotocol\/set(timeout:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketProtocol"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO14SocketProtocolPAAE3set7timeoutySi_tF","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"set(timeout:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"timeout"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the time in seconds after which I\/O operations on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"socket"},{"text":" will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"time out if they have not yet completed.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"timeout","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On a blocking socket, this means that any blocking "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Socket","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"operation will time out after "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"type":"text","text":" seconds of inactivity,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returning "},{"code":"timedOut","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","